Most importantly the
satisfaction of knowing
that I can go out,

45:59.708 --> 46:04.210
I can get what I need to
live the life that I wanna
live here at Calico Bluff,

46:05.080 --> 46:09.048
this is the payoff
for all that work and I'd do
it 100 times over to get a

46:09.084 --> 46:11.818
good piece of meat like this.

46:12.053 --> 46:16.756
So, there's nothing
better than fresh meat
after a hard day's work.

